  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kaamos is a bite-sized turn-based puzzle roguelike where battles are fought by matching tiles on a grid with looping rows and columns. Build your character and deck of tiles by looting equipment from your foes. Traverse a dark medieval world where the Sun went down and never rose again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/3a67ff5ca9cca486b5737fa1bd0c2e47.poster.avif?t=1772564828\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/3a67ff5ca9cca486b5737fa1bd0c2e47.webm?t=1772564828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/3a67ff5ca9cca486b5737fa1bd0c2e47.mp4?t=1772564828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/5fc106813b58f377918d2c5e490caf20.avif?t=1772564828\" width=616 height=80 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face hostile opponents in duels to the death where you see enemy actions in advance. Match tiles of the same color on a grid where dragging a row or column loops it back on the other side in order to counter the incoming onslaught of enemy attacks. Stab, crush and cleave your way to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/6b73871b8a9bedef7a5e7d55c57914a4.poster.avif?t=1772564828\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/6b73871b8a9bedef7a5e7d55c57914a4.webm?t=1772564828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/6b73871b8a9bedef7a5e7d55c57914a4.mp4?t=1772564828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/d99330397b79344f2fdf0879d64268a8.avif?t=1772564828\" width=616 height=80 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip powerful weapons, armor, and rings to change your tactics and tile selection for battles. Want to be a dual-wielding berserker, an evasive duelist, or a knight clad in heavy armor? With over 180 items there are interesting build choices and playstyles for every player.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/f3d9b5efc5bccd736466510cc72ccbfb.poster.avif?t=1772564828\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/f3d9b5efc5bccd736466510cc72ccbfb.webm?t=1772564828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/f3d9b5efc5bccd736466510cc72ccbfb.mp4?t=1772564828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/6fa158ada83bd68768bfc4072628fd30.avif?t=1772564828\" width=616 height=80 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate a randomly generated dark medieval world filled with madness. Unravel the mystery behind the disappearance of the Sun or fade into the darkness. You are not alone. There’s always something lurking in the dark behind every fork in the path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/bfd4d32cacd403f4e9a26848d5d4e3f5.poster.avif?t=1772564828\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/bfd4d32cacd403f4e9a26848d5d4e3f5.webm?t=1772564828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/bfd4d32cacd403f4e9a26848d5d4e3f5.mp4?t=1772564828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kaamos is a bite-sized turn-based puzzle roguelike where battles are fought by matching tiles on a grid with looping rows and columns. Build your character and deck of tiles by looting equipment from your foes. Traverse a dark medieval world where the Sun went down and never rose again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/3a67ff5ca9cca486b5737fa1bd0c2e47.poster.avif?t=1772564828\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/3a67ff5ca9cca486b5737fa1bd0c2e47.webm?t=1772564828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/3a67ff5ca9cca486b5737fa1bd0c2e47.mp4?t=1772564828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/5fc106813b58f377918d2c5e490caf20.avif?t=1772564828\" width=616 height=80 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face hostile opponents in duels to the death where you see enemy actions in advance. Match tiles of the same color on a grid where dragging a row or column loops it back on the other side in order to counter the incoming onslaught of enemy attacks. Stab, crush and cleave your way to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/6b73871b8a9bedef7a5e7d55c57914a4.poster.avif?t=1772564828\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/6b73