. There’s always something lurking in the dark behind every fork in the path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/bfd4d32cacd403f4e9a26848d5d4e3f5.poster.avif?t=1772564828\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/bfd4d32cacd403f4e9a26848d5d4e3f5.webm?t=1772564828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/bfd4d32cacd403f4e9a26848d5d4e3f5.mp4?t=1772564828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
